	<Title>
		Caffeine: Can it help me lose weight?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Caffeine may help you lose a little weight, but it also comes with some downsides.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Does caffeine help with weight loss?
	</Question>
